TITLE: Retrieving Relevant Memories Using Vector Similarity
DESCRIPTION: Function that retrieves memories relevant to a query by generating an embedding for the query and searching for similar memories using vector similarity matching.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza/blob/main/docs/docs/guides/memory-management.md#2025-04-16_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
async function retrieveRelevantMemories(runtime: AgentRuntime, query: string) {
    const embedding = await runtime.embed(query);

    return await runtime.messageManager.searchMemoriesByEmbedding(embedding, {
        match_threshold: 0.8,
        count: 10,
        include_metadata: true
    });
}
```

