TITLE: Implementing PDF Processing Service in Eliza
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create a custom PdfService for handling PDF document analysis. The service extracts text content from all pages of a PDF document for further processing.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza/blob/main/docs/notes/advanced.md#2025-04-16_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
class PdfService extends Service {
    async convertPdfToText(pdfBuffer: Buffer): Promise<string> {
        const pdf = await getDocument({ data: pdfBuffer }).promise;
        const numPages = pdf.numPages;
        const textPages = [];

        for (let pageNum = 1; pageNum <= numPages; pageNum++) {
            const page = await pdf.getPage(pageNum);
            const textContent = await page.getTextContent();
            const pageText = textContent.items
                .filter(isTextItem)
                .map((item) => item.str)
                .join(" ");
            textPages.push(pageText);
        }

        return textPages.join("\n");
    }
}
```

