TITLE: Ensuring Participant Exists in Room
DESCRIPTION: Method to ensure a participant exists in a room. If the participant doesn't exist, they are added to the room using the database service.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza/blob/main/docs/api/classes/AgentRuntime.md#2025-04-16_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
async ensureParticipantExists(userId: `${string}-${string}-${string}-${string}-${string}`, roomId: `${string}-${string}-${string}-${string}-${string}`): Promise<void> {
  const database = this.getService<DatabaseService>(ServiceType.DATABASE);
