TITLE: Resource Management Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Client resource management implementation with connection cleanup and reconnection logic.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza/blob/main/docs/notes/packages/clients.md#2025-04-16_snippet_23

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
class ClientManager {
    private async cleanup() {
        // Close connections
        await Promise.all(this.connections.map((conn) => conn.close()));

        // Clear caches
        this.cache.clear();

        // Cancel timers
        this.timers.forEach((timer) => clearInterval(timer));
    }

    private async reconnect() {
        await this.cleanup();
        await wait(this.calculateBackoff());
        await this.initialize();
    }
}
```

