TITLE: Implementing Service Registration in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to properly register a service in ElizaOS, including checking for existing registrations to avoid duplicates.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza/blob/main/docs/notes/plugins.md#2025-04-16_snippet_31

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// Proper service registration
registerService(service: Service): void {
    const serviceType = (service as typeof Service).serviceType;
    if (this.services.has(serviceType)) {
        console.warn(`Service ${serviceType} is already registered`);
        return;
    }
    this.services.set(serviceType, service);
}
```

