TITLE: Creating the JSDoc Generation Workflow Inputs - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet describes the inputs required for the JSDoc generation GitHub Actions workflow. It specifies parameters like 'pull_number', 'root_directory', 'excluded_directories', and 'reviewers', detailing their purposes and default values.
