TITLE: Validating NASA API Configuration
DESCRIPTION: TypeScript function for validating NASA API configuration, ensuring the API key is properly set before attempting API calls.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza/blob/main/docs/docs/tutorials/nader_tutorial_35min.md#2025-04-16_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const validateNasaConfig = (runtime: IAgentRuntime) => {
    const config = {
        apiKey: runtime.getSetting("NASA_API_KEY")
    };
    if (!config.apiKey) {
        throw new Error("NASA API key not configured");
    }
    return config;
};
```

